name: Madam M (Final Fantasy 7 Remale) NSFW / SFW 3D
description:
Hello my friends!

Today we have Madam M, reputable massage parlor from Final Fantasy 7 and pure oriental style milf :3

It was trained on animefull.ckpt with clip skip 2. It works well with such 3D model.

0.7 - 0.95 strength of Lora is the best radius. I prefer 0.85.

Some necessary tokens for better experience:

MadamM, mature female, brown hair, hair bun, hair ornament, lipstick, makeup, black eyeshadow, eyelashes, brown eyes

Usually I add:

ultra detail hair, ultra realistic hair, ultra detail face, perfect face, perfect eyes

For her clothes and accesories:
japanese clothes, obi, intricate black kimono, bare shoulders, hand fan

Also you can use other tokens or make her naked and experiment.

Also LoRA trained with some NSFW arts but I didn't test in special poses with males at this time.

Advices for better experience:

·         use highres.fix (If you are sure that your prompt is easy for SD); I prefer x4_Fatal_anime_500000_G, lollypop and animesharp.

use extention "dddetailer" (very useful extension for faces. You forget about face inpainting with it).

·         use SD Upscale script in img2img (For me 1.25-1.5x with AnimeSharp, UltraSharp or fatal anime is good on 0.2-0.3 denoising strengh);

·         use Ultimate SD Upscale script in img2img with controlnet (tile) for more details if you upscale to 4K or more.

·         Use inpaint and sketch (or Photopea) for other details;

·         Use Photoshop / Photopea extension.

I will be glad to receive feedback from you and a demonstration of your art with my LoRA!

Other works.
